OL,3,CPolice probe into more than 200 deaths
OL,4,Cor injuries at major NHS Trust
OL,6,FPolice are looking at more than 200
OL,7,Fcases of death or injury as a result
OL,8,Fof surgery at one of the South-East's
OL,9,Fbiggest NHS Trusts, it's being
OL,10,Freported.
OL,12,FThe figure has doubled since police
OL,13,Flaunched the investigation in 2023.
OL,14,FOperation Bramber initially identified
OL,15,F105 cases of allegations of poor care
OL,16,Fand practice within University
OL,17,FHospitals Sussex NHS Trust.
OL,19,FIt comes after whistleblowers raised
OL,20,Fconcerns about general surgery and
OL,21,Fneurosurgery.
