OL,3,CPolice probe into more than 200 deaths
OL,4,Cor injuries at major NHS Trust
OL,6,FOn top of the reported 200 cases of
OL,7,Falleged medical negligence, ITV News
OL,8,FMeridian understands that Sussex
OL,9,FPolice has taken more than 130
OL,10,Fstatements and produced 550 reports
OL,11,Ffrom interviews with those connected
OL,12,Fto the investigation.
OL,14,FNo arrests have yet been made.
OL,16,FThe father of Lewis Chilcott, 23, from
OL,17,FBillingshurst, say he feels let down
OL,18,Fafter waiting for answers into his
OL,19,Fdeath.
