OL,6,FLewis had a tracheostomy at the
OL,7,FPrincess Royal in Haywards Heath and
OL,8,Fwas then transferred to Royal Sussex
OL,9,FCounty Hospital in Brighton, where he
OL,10,Fdied.
OL,12,FSimon Chilcott claims his son's death
OL,13,Fwas caused by alleged errors during
OL,14,Fhis treatment.
OL,16,FHe said: "It's all these other stories
OL,17,Fcoming out and it confirms to me that
OL,18,Fthe things are not right there.
