OL,6,FNisha Sharma, principal lawyer at
OL,7,FSlater and Gordon, is handling a
OL,8,Fgrowing number of cases which form
OL,9,Fpart of Operation Bramber.
OL,11,FShe said: "It is truly heartbreaking
OL,12,Fand we only hope they received the
OL,13,Fanswers they need and deserve through
OL,14,Fthis police investigation. We are
OL,15,Fsupporting them in every way we can.
OL,17,F"To anyone who has yet to come
OL,18,Fforward, who has concerns over the
OL,19,Fcare they received from University
OL,20,FHospitals Sussex, we would urge them
OL,21,Fto do so.
