OL,6,F"Operation Bramber is clearly at least
OL,7,Ftwice as big as when it first
OL,8,Flaunched, so it is vital we understand
OL,9,Fthe true scale of what we truly face
OL,10,Fand that those involved have proper
OL,11,Frepresentation."
OL,13,FA team of specialist consultant
OL,14,Fsurgeons, independent of University
OL,15,FHospitals Sussex, have been drafted
OL,16,Fin, to provide their expert opinion.
OL,18,FTheir findings will be considered by
OL,19,Fthe police alongside other information
OL,20,Fto determine whether criminal charges
OL,21,Fwill follow.
