OL,6,FA spokesperson for Sussex Police said:
OL,7,F"A dedicated team of officers are
OL,8,Fprogressing enquiries and engaging
OL,9,Fwith involved patients and families to
OL,10,Fprovide information and support while
OL,11,Fthis is ongoing.
OL,13,F"Cases that do not currently meet a
OL,14,Fcriminal threshold will be withdrawn,
OL,15,Fand this will be communicated to
OL,16,Fpatients and families directly by the
OL,17,Finvestigation team.
OL,19,F"Sussex Police is committed to
OL,20,Fconducting a thorough and transparent
OL,21,Finvestigation.
