OL,4,Cor injuries at major NHS Trust
OL,6,F"Due to the complex nature of the
OL,7,Fenquiries, this is likely to take some
OL,8,Ftime to complete."
OL,10,FProfessor Katie Urch, Chief Medical
OL,11,FOfficer, University Hospitals Sussex,
OL,12,Fsaid: "I know this is a really
OL,13,Fdifficult time for everyone involved
OL,14,Fin these investigations and understand
OL,15,Fhow painful the process can be.
OL,17,F"Patient care is always our priority,
OL,18,Fand we are continually working to
OL,19,Fimprove services and people's
OL,20,Fexperience of them.
